 />\n唔該自己去日領事館申請"},{"pid":"9abd684fc6b6e2201cc7df9a032194c7ee524bcc","tid":1911391,"uid":348941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:14:01.000Z","msg":"就算俾你入到境都要強制隔離14日啊 入嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fe8e1c3ddbf3a11e3d056972ae2c0cb8335e8d","tid":1911391,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5c22d44cd791ee32e27bb56bd175f9d4e53d225","tid":1911391,"uid":156092,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:04:23.000Z","msg":"吊你啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:25:34.000Z","msg":"吊你老母"},{"pid":"189d56027a7ec11fb6b5034119fd219c9f182a9f","tid":1911391,"uid":5125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"呢個時候仲想周圍去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8fb079fa01224dfc45e31b0ce59c5edf623b3f","tid":1911391,"uid":156281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1515a5d044cb592ba76e7dc3bbcc1f0447162e61","tid":1911391,"uid":269810,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:29:32.000Z","msg":"日本理9你特衰定BNO咩，兩款都計香港計中蟈囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMWRpbP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMWRpbP.jpg&h=9cf6ef66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85fb35fbf9d0ee63414664832ef539292373394f","tid":1911391,"uid":12130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n聯署要求英國政府賦予BNO持有人居英權及工作權<br />\n🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧<br />\n《香港法案》如獲通過 持BNO港人可獲居英權<br />\n<br />\n英國自由民主黨議員Alistair Carmichael日前向下議院提交《香港法案》，為BNO持有人爭取權益。議員表示該黨一向支持BNO平權，加上中國破壞《中英聯合聲明》協議，故希望透過法案為持有BNO的港人爭取居英權、工作權，並重新啟動BNO申請。有關法案2月25日於英國下議院首讀通過，並定於6月12日進行二讀。如法案通過，持BNO港人有望獲取居英權，而回歸前出生又未曾申請BNO人士亦有機會可重新遞交申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/article/147958/熱話/bno平權-法案-首讀-英下議院-二讀-港人-居英權/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2Farticle%2F147958%2F%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2Fbno%E5%B9%B3%E6%AC%8A-%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E9%A6%96%E8%AE%80-%E8%8B%B1%E4%B8%8B%E8%AD%B0%E9%99%A2-%E4%BA%8C%E8%AE%80-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E5%B1%85%E8%8B%B1%E6%AC%8A%2F&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=d74dd58b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/article/147958/熱話/bno平權-法案-首讀-英下議院-二讀-港人-居英權/</a><br />\n🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧<br />\n⚠️我唔係British citizen簽唔簽得？<br />\n✅過往一直有兩三次都係咁簽，英政府一直都照接受簽名，所以當然簽得。<br />\n-<br />\n⚠️Postal Code係咩啊？<br />\n✅你填WC2N 5DU就得。<br />\n🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧<br />\n最後希望大家快啲share出去啦！<br />\n🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/300091\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F300091&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=cd270c0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/300091</a>"},{"pid":"86d340ab1a906469a48c5cc05e51cb958c42861d","tid":1911391,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T08:49:31.000Z","msg":"你係英女皇咪比你入"}]}